      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary by The Associated Press on Wednesday about Ben Weisman, a songwriter, included erroneous information from a family member about his illnesses before his death. He suffered a stroke and had pneumonia; he did not have Alzheimer's disease. The obituary also erroneously included a group among the performers for whom he wrote songs. He did not write for the Beatles.</p>
      </block>
